Package: bookprep
Title: Prepares a bookdown project from a skeleton and a
    template
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Marion",
           family = "Louveaux",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "marion.louveaux@gmail.com",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-1794-3748"))
Description: Prepares a bookdown project from a customizable
    bookdown skeleton and, if needed, a template for the chapters. Helps
    creating reproducible yet flexible bookdown projects, for instance to
    deliver data analyses to customers following a standardized format.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://marionlouveaux.github.io/bookprep/,
